Project Overview
This repository contains the implementation of a Sales Dashboard for the AdventureWorksDW2019 dataset, focusing on Reseller Sales.
The dashboard provides key performance indicators (KPIs) and visualizations that help analyze the sales performance across different dimensions such as Sales, resellers, products, geographic regions, and time periods.
The purpose of this project is to showcase data analysis and visualization skills, particularly in sales analytics, using Power BI and DAX.
- Power BI Desktop Microsoft - Ver Sep 2024
- [Dataset AdventureWorksDW2019](https://github.com/Microsoft/sql-server-samples/releases/download/adventureworks/AdventureWorksDW2019.bak)
- Tools and Technologies
   Power BI: For creating interactive visualizations and dashboards.
   DAX (Data Analysis Expressions): To calculate custom measures and KPIs.
   AdventureWorksDW2019: As the data source for sales analysis.
- How to Use :
   Clone the repository to your local machine.
   Open the Power BI file (.pbix) and connect it to the AdventureWorksDW2019 dataset.
   Explore the pre-built visualizations and KPIs, or customize them further based on your requirements.
   Review the DAX formulas used to create measures for the KPIs and other analytics.
- Future Improvements
   Adding more detailed analysis on Customer Sales alongside Reseller Sales.
   Expanding the dashboard to include forecasting models for future sales predictions.
   Implementing dynamic filtering and more advanced interaction options within the dashboard.
